to use this project you should have somehings intalled such as 

* python <obviously>
* install git
* install latest version of curl <make sure it's installed in C drive 
                                  using this command
                                  
                                  
only after then we can use the python command properly

create a file and name it to anthing <as an example : python sender>
    curl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py -o get-pip.py

    python get-pip.py

    python -m pip install pyautogui

    Cd '' the trajectory of your file '' 

    git clone https://github.com/hoppuman/TikTokHack.git

    Cd '' the trajectory of the file downloaded '' 

put what ever you desire to be sent to your friend

    python shrek.py
   
after sending that command you only got 2 seconds for it to start

if you wish for it to stop quickly switch to the console and click on < ctrl + c >
